OL,3,C20 people jailed over abuse of girls
OL,4,Cin 1990s and 2000s
OL,6,FTwenty people have been given jail
OL,7,Fsentences totalling more than 270
OL,8,Fyears for grooming and sexually
OL,9,Fabusing three girls in the 1990s and
OL,10,F2000s.
OL,12,FThe offences were committed in
OL,13,FDewsbury and Batley, West Yorkshire,
OL,14,Fagainstvictims who were as young as
OL,15,F12, between 1995 and 2003.
OL,17,FThe defendants were convicted
OL,18,Ffollowing six separate trials between
OL,19,F2023 and 2024.
