OL,6,FReporting of the sentences, the last
OL,7,Fof which was handed down last year,
OL,8,Fhas been restricted until now.
OL,10,FThe sentences were as follows:
OL,12,FTwo other men were found by a court to
OL,13,Fhave committed sexual offences but
OL,14,Fwere judged unfit to enter pleas.
OL,16,FDet Ch Insp Rob Stevens, of Kirklees
OL,17,FDistrict Police, said: "This has been
OL,18,Fa major investigation into truly
OL,19,Fappalling sexual abuse of vulnerable
OL,20,Fgirls in Kirklees by a large number of
OL,21,Fsexual predators.
