OL,3,C20 people jailed over abuse of girls
OL,4,Cin 1990s and 2000s
OL,6,F"Over an almost two-year period,
OL,7,Fjuries have heard some shocking
OL,8,Frevelations about the dreadful way
OL,9,Fvictims were abused by those involved.
OL,11,F"They were repeatedly sexually
OL,12,Fassaulted, in some cases given Class A
OL,13,Fdrugs, and very much treated as
OL,14,Fcommodities for the gratification of
OL,15,Fheartless predators."
OL,17,FHe praised the "enormous bravery" of
OL,18,Fthe victims.
